[normal] first five recommendations in the Strategy are assigned to Business to take forward, and this includes recommendation 4 which is to "address gender bias".
[normal] 
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]17.
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]The Department 
[normal]for Employment and Learning Northern Ireland 
